<topic id="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable">
  <title>WebHelp Responsive Layout Reusable Content</title>
  <shortdesc>Reusable content for WebHelp Responsive Layout and Features chapter.</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <p id="p_o3l_bgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_p3l_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="publication-title">
          <dt>Publication Title</dt>
          <dd>The title of the publication. It is usually taken from the DITA map title.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="main-page-logo">
          <dt>Logo</dt>
          <dd>
            <p id="p_q3l_bgk_54b">Displays a logo associated with the publication. Additionally, you can set a target
              URL that will be opened when you click on the logo image.</p>
            <p id="p_r3l_bgk_54b">The logo image can be specified using the <xref
                href="../../topics/webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters.dita#webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters/logo-image"
                  ><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-output-parameters/ph_webhelp_logo_image">
                  <ph/>
                </ph> transformation parameter</xref>. For the target URL, use the <xref
                href="../../topics/webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters.dita#webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters/logo-image-target-url"
                  ><ph
                  conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-output-parameters/ph_webhelp_logo_image_target_url"/>
                parameter</xref>.</p>
          </dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="publication-menu">
          <dt>Menu</dt>
          <dd>Helps you to navigate to your documentation. This component presents a set of links to
            all topics from your publication. For information about customizing the menu, see <xref
              keyref="whr-customize-menu"/> topic.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="search-query-input">
          <dt>Search Input</dt>
          <dd>An input text field where you can enter search queries.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="main-page-footer">
          <dt>Page Footer</dt>
          <dd>WebHelp Responsive output footer. </dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="print-icon">
          <dt>Print Link</dt>
          <dd>A print icon that opens the print dialog box for your particular browser. </dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="index-terms-link">
          <dt>Index Terms Link</dt>
          <dd>Presents a link to the index terms page. You can control if this component is
            displayed by using the <xref
              href="../../topics/webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters.dita#webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters/show-indexterms-link"
                ><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-output-parameters/ph_webhelp_show_indexterms_link"
              /> parameter</xref>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="theme-button">
          <dt>Switch Theme Button</dt>
          <dd>Presents a button opening a drop-down menu for selecting the theme. You can control if
            this component is displayed by using the <xref
              href="../../topics/webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters.dita#webhelp-responsive-plugin-additional-parameters/webhelp_enable_dark_mode"
                ><ph conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-output-parameters/ph_webhelp_enable_dark_mode"/>
              parameter</xref>. For more information, see <xref
              href="../../topics/webhelp-enabling-dark-mode.dita"/>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
</topic>
